                                "stop": 9.254,
                                "byte_start": 85163,
                                "byte_stop": 122257,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court, in No. 02-337, Breuer versus Jim\u0027s Concrete of Brevard, Inc. will be announced by Justice Souter."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.254,
                        "stop": 188.003,
